âœ” Legitimate files can be weaponized as covert containers

ğŸ“š Lessons Learned
NTFS ADS is a powerful anti-forensics technique
Hidden data does not alter visible file size or behavior
PowerShell can uncover stealth persistence mechanisms
ADS should always be checked during forensic investigations
